<br>
I've been batting around the idea of running another D20 campaign sometime in the future.  This will in NO WAY conflict with or even begin prior to the completion of our on going Victorian Vampire campaign.  However, I would like to get an idea for what people would like to play vs. what I am willing to run.  The options I can think of are continuing with the old characters from Iron Kingdoms, starting new IK characters (since new material is out), Ravenloft, Scarred Lands (WW's fantasy setting), Forgotten Realm, or Spycraft/Shadowforce Archer.<br>
<br>
You guys let me know which you'd like or present new ideas or just tell me to foff (I'm opening myself up for this one I guess).<br>
<br>
