<br>
Personally, I would like to see a return to the Fantasy RPG.  This genre is like Taco Bell.  One could not live off of it, but you do have the cravings now and then.  Of course, that is where the similarities end.  I doubt seriously if there is a RPG out there that causes one to shit all night.  I digress....<br>
<br>
If you want my vote I would say let's try out Scarred Lands and maybe add a dash of Savage Species to the mix.<br>
<br>
