<br>
Ravenloft is not a bad idea, but I would prefer a world that is not based on one foreboding concept. <p></p><i></i></td></tr></table> </td></tr></table> <table border=0 width=95%><tr><td align=left valign="top"> </td><td align=right valign="top"><a href="http://pub70.ezboard.com/fheavyhand65062frm15.showPrevMessage?topicID=40.topic"> << Prev Topic</a>&nbsp;| <a href="http://pub70.ezboard.com/fheavyhand65062frm15.showNextMessage?topicID=40.topic"> Next Topic >> </a><br><br><a self href=http://pub70.ezboard.com/fheavyhand65062frm15.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=40.topic&index=3><img src=http://heavyhand.org/buttonreply2.gif border=0 alt="Add Reply"></a> </td></tr></table><br><table width=95% border=0><td valign="top"> <a href=http://pub70.ezboard.com/fheavyhand65062frm15.emailToFriend?topicID=40.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/image/email.gif border=0 alt="Email This To a Friend"> Email This To a Friend</a><br> <a href=http://pub70.ezboard.com/fheavyhand65062frm15.threadControl?topicID=40.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/black_default/deleteThread.gif border=0 alt="Topic Control Image"> Topic Commands</a><br> <a href=http://pub70.ezboard.com/fheavyhand65062frm15.subscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=40.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/ultimate/subscribe.gif width=20 height=20 border=0 alt="Click to receive email notification of replies"> Click to receive email notification of replies</a> <br>  <a href=http://pub70.ezboard.com/fheavyhand65062frm15.unsubscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=40.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/ultimate/unsubscribe.gif width=20 height=20 border=0 alt="Click to stop receiving email notification of replies"> Click to stop receiving email notification of replies</a> <br> </td><td align="right" valign="top"></td></tr><tr align="right"><td colspan=2><form action=http://pub70.ezboard.com/BBSForum.jumpShowForum method=post><table border="0" cellspacing="0" 